title: ToDieForDS-CG.avi
description:
To Die For 1988

L.A. real estate agent Kate Wooten gets a new lease on life when she learns that her new client,
a mysterious and handsome man named Vlad, is looking for a house isolated in the Hollywood Hills
where he wants to live and doesn't want to be disturbed.
It doesn't take long for Kate to fall in love with her new client and to learn that he's a real vampire
